step_data.thought:
I've successfully navigated to the Bestsellers Report page and have filled in both the required date fields:
1. 'From' date: 2023-01-01
2. 'To' date: 2023-12-31

Now that I have set the date range for the report, I need to click the 'Show Report' button to generate the bestsellers report. This will display the top-selling products within the specified date range. The 'Show Report' button has ID 742, so I'll click on it to generate the report.
